rows.label: qst104206_msg0001
rows.name:
I was so disappointed when I heard
that Acedia was gone.

rows.label: qst104206_msg0002
rows.name:
I was just getting ready to start
attending the Academy there...

rows.label: qst104206_msg0003
rows.name:
So I'll do everything I can to help!
I'll even do heavy lifting!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0101
rows.name:
Did you bring me some wood?
I'll take whatever you've got!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0121
rows.name:
I still need more wood,
so keep it coming!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0151
rows.name:
Nice, that should be all the
wood I need! Thanks!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0201
rows.name:
I'm still disappointed I won't be able to
go to the famous Acedian Academy...

rows.label: qst104206_msg0202
rows.name:
But hey, it'll be way more fun starting
up a new school here instead!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0251
rows.name:
Hummer knows how to make the most
of all kinds of different materials!
He's pretty amazing...
